{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_01","textHome":"哼！哼哼…！好…！太好了…！下次活动的梗@就决定是这个了……啊！干嘛？不要跑到别人@的城堡，还偷听别人自言自语啊！还有那表情@也太失礼了！我叫都雏乃，姑且算是部长吧。@哈？化学部啦，这里是化学部的活动室。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_18","textHome":"攀登？爆破？无论多么高的墙壁，@都有跨越的方法。墙那头的景色，@就是对努力过的人最高的褒奖。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_19","textHome":"化学和人……都有无限可能！未来是光明的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_20","textHome":"这、这样一来……我也能变成@适合穿白衣的性感理科女生了吗！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_21","textHome":"我要是示弱了，后辈们也会不安吧。@所以我，要一直保持帅气的前辈形象才行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_22","textHome":"我想要长大！变成伟大的都前辈！但是我，@并不是想要被人尊敬。我想成为能接受大家@所有的不安和悲伤的——那样巨大的前辈！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_23","textHome":"浓缩就是精华！拥有庞大的知识储备和熟练@精湛的技能，就不得不接受个子小这种短板。@不过话说回来，小小的身体却饱含无限能量，@这样的反差萌不是最棒了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":300300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_24","textHome":"怎么样，今天也有享受夏天吗？@在实验室的时候要慎重，在海滩上就要大胆！@这就是我目标中的性感系科学家！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_25","textHome":"趁着早上，去海边游会儿泳吧……@等太阳再高一点，@带着孩子的还有情侣们就要涌进去了，@那就太拥挤了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_26","textHome":"太阳升高了，就要提前做好紫外线的防范哦。@「不会被阳光晒的药」暂时还做不出来哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_27","textHome":"傍晚化学部的部室，@似乎是只有我一个人的城堡……@暑假就更是如此了。@也就偶尔衣美里会来玩。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_03","textHome":"并不是我的威严不够，是那家伙太狂妄了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_28","textHome":"什么……已经深夜了吗？@没办法，再学习一会儿就睡吧……@如果因为是暑假就偷懒的话，@就没法给后辈树立榜样了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_29","textHome":"呜，好热……好想去别墅乘凉啊。@啊，“别墅”指的是学校图书馆啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_30","textHome":"好啦，该出门了。不对，不是去泳池！@是魔女退治的巡逻！@就算是暑假，犯傻也要有个度啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_31","textHome":"接下来，差不多该去无尽境界了吧？@要是魔法少女的复制品也受不了夏天的话，@说不定就会变弱了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_32","textHome":"魔法少女们的团队战……@嘛，只要是可爱后辈的请求，@我都会乐意效劳的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_33","textHome":"哼哼哼……快看！我这大胆又华丽的泳装！@完全就是夏日的炸药，海岸边的硝化甘油啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_34","textHome":"啊——我一直都想飒爽地走在岸边。@不管怎么样今年我买到了15厘米的增高……@啊，不是，是厚底的沙滩凉鞋！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_35","textHome":"呜哇，你在干什么！不要突然往我这泼水啊！@要是再这样恶作剧的话，@我就要用我特别定制的喷灯来喷火……@不对，是喷水了啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_36","textHome":"不能因为来了海边，就一个劲的玩啊。@海滩上也可能会出现魔女，@到那时候就该我出场了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_37","textHome":"在海边表演「有趣的化学实验」，@应该也会很有趣吧。@夏天，有很多人是带着孩子来玩的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":1}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_00_04","textHome":"居然利用化学来夺人性命……不可饶恕！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_38","textHome":"我离自己目标的理想身材还差的很远……@不过我已经等不及完成目标了。@要问为什么的话，@我十几岁的夏天已经所剩无几了吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_39","textHome":"好想在岸边的阳伞下，@喝一杯无酒精混合饮料奢侈一下啊。@什么，不许说“小孩子就喝麦茶吧”这种话！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_40","textHome":"衣美里和梨花也邀请了我来海边……@但要是我被误认为是其中谁的妹妹，@那可就是我身为前辈的屈辱了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3003_51_41","textHome":"喂喂！不要摸我的头啊！@难道说……@你是在我具有炸药般破坏力的身材面前@害羞了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300300}]},{"autoTurn